r shows that a battle continues to rage today not between two varieties of true christianity but between truth and error light and darkness good and evil product information▼▲ format paperbacknumber of pages vendor banner of truthpublication date isbn isbn  other customers also purchased add to cart add to wishlist ezekiel interpretation commentary joseph blenkinsopp joseph blenkinsopp westminster john knox press    hardcover  retail  save   add to cart add to wishlist both sides now peter barnes peter barnes banner of truth  trade paperback  retail  save   add to cart add to wishlist holy spirit in the wesleyan heritage teacher revised abingdon press    trade paperback  retail  save   add to cart add to wishlist through fire and water an overview of mennonite history revised harry loewen steven m nolt harry loewen steven m nolt herald press    trade paperback  retail  save    stars out of   reviews related products add to cart add to wishlist christianity and liberalism revised j gresham machen j gresham machen wm b eerdmans publishing co    trade paperback  retail  save    stars out of   reviews add to cart add to wishlist the universe next door a basic worldview catalog james w sire james w sire ivp academic    trade paperback  retail  save    stars out of   reviews add to cart add to wishlist worshipping the state how liberalism became our state religion benjamin wiker benjamin wiker regnery publishing    hardcover  retail  save   add to cart add to wishlist family worship bible guide reformation heritage  soli deo gloria    hardcover  retail  save   author bio▼▲ peter barnes is a presbyterian pastor who lives in sydney australia he ministers at revesby presbyterian church and lectures in church history at the presbyterian theological college in burwood he is married to lyn and they have six children product reviews▼▲ be the first to write a review write review ask a question▼▲ have a question about this product ask us here find related products▼▲ books ebooks  